des:
This ain't your grandma's Winchat App! Soon you'll be the talk of the town when you spout out some of the amazing facts you'll learn about the incredible Winchat through this amazing app.
 
In case you're wondering here are some of YOUR GRANDMA'S WHINCHAT FACTS!!!!!! 
Fact 1! Never trust a Whinchat wearing socks. 
Fact 2! If Whinchats are in your house making a mess... Call them dust birds! 
Fact 3! Whinchats chat with the wind. Thanks for seeing your grandma's whinchat facts!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
